resources.name: /users
resources.description: ### POST /users ### Example of request body: ``` { "email": "example@email.com", "password": "Example123", "is_adm": true, "name": "Example Name", "cpf": "123456789-00", "profile_img": "url_here" } ``` cpf and profile_img are optional fields. is_adm is also optional and defaults to false. Example response: ``` { "id": "example_user_uuid", "email": "example@email.com", "password": "Example123", "is_adm": true, "name": "Example Name", "cpf": "123456789-00", "profile_img": "url_here", "review": null, "pets": [], "reservations": [] } ```

resources.name: /users
resources.description: ### GET /users ### ###### Requires authentication ###### Returns data of logged in user. If user is admin, returns data of all users. ##### Standard user response: ##### ``` { "id": "6fbaddd5-64fa-4a32-98a3-6f10b4c284fe", "name": "Example Name", "email": "example@mail.com", "is_adm": false, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "img_url" } ``` ##### Admin response: ##### ``` [ { "id": "6fbaddd5-64fa-4a32-98a3-6f10b4c284fe", "name": "Example Name", "email": "example@mail.com", "is_adm": false, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "img_url" }, { "id": "6fbaddd5-64fa-4a32-98a3-6f10b4c284fe", "name": "Second User", "email": "example2@mail.com", "is_adm": false, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "url_here" }, ... ] ```

resources.name: /users/:id
resources.description: ### PATCH /users ### ###### Requires authentication ###### Update informations of the logged in user. Editable fields: - name - email - cpf - profile_img Example of request body: ``` { "name": "New Name", "profile_img": "new_img_url" } ``` Example response: ``` { "id": "6fbaddd5-64fa-4a32-98a3-6f10b4c284fe", "name": "New Name", "email": "example@mail.com", "is_adm": false, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "new_img_url" } ```

resources.name: /users/:id
resources.description: ### DELETE /users/:id ### ###### Requires authentication ###### On success, returns status code 204.

resources.name: /pets
resources.description: ### POST /pets ### ###### Requires authentication ###### Example of request body: ``` { "name": "Pet Name", "type": "dog", "age": "5 months", "neutered": false, "vaccinated": true, "docile": true } ``` Example response: ``` { "id": "dbdf6daa-f626-40ec-aa7d-49d3548dbb96", "name": "Pet Name", "type": "dog", "age": "5 months", "neutered": false, "vaccinated": true, "docile": true, "user": { "id": "6fbaddd5-64fa-4a32-98a3-6f10b4c284fe", "name": "New Name", "email": "zezinho@mail.com", "is_adm": false, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "new_img_url" } } ```

resources.name: /pets
resources.description: ### GET /pets ### ###### Requires authentication ###### Returns all pets of the logged in user. If user is admin, returns all registered pets. Example of response body: ``` [ { "id": "262991e7-ebe0-4c40-bc5c-388e041fe136", "name": "doguinho", "type": "dog", "age": "5 anos", "neutered": true, "vaccinated": true, "docile": true, "owner": { "id": "3d0badb3-831f-465a-9916-16bac7b9149a", "name": "New Name", "email": "nicholas.ge1301@gmail.com", "is_adm": true, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "new_img_url" } }, { "id": "8b884f82-2fd0-43a8-98fa-eec3c39f9236", "name": "otro dog", "type": "dog", "age": "5 meses", "neutered": true, "vaccinated": true, "docile": true, "owner": { "id": "3d0badb3-831f-465a-9916-16bac7b9149a", "name": "New Name", "email": "nicholas.ge1301@gmail.com", "is_adm": true, "cpf": null, "profile_img": "new_img_url" } }, ... ```

resources.name: /pets/:id
resources.description: ### PATCH /pet/:id ### ###### Requires authentication ###### Editable fields: - name - vaccinated - neutered - docile Example of request body: ``` { "vaccinated": true, "neutered": true } ``` Example response: ``` { "id": "6d324bed-d055-4fbb-a38f-dbc34ab8c226", "name": "Pet Name", "type": "dog", "age": "5 months", "neutered": true, "vaccinated": true, "docile": true } ```

resources.name: /pets/:id
resources.description: ### DELETE /pets/:id ### ###### Requires authentication ###### Pets which have already been booked for a resevation cannot be deleted (even if said reservation has alreaedy been cancelled). On success, returns status code 204.
